"I had the same error. There were two lines missing in .arduino15/packages/esp32/hardware/esp32/2.0.17/boards.txt:

lilygo_t_display.upload.flags=
lilygo_t_display.upload.extra_flags=

Lines added, IDE restarted, uploading worked..."

[https://forum.arduino.cc/t/how-to-display-image-on-ttgo-t-display-esp32/1174923/2]

---

Stay with esp32 version 2.0.17

"Note: Since version 3.0.0 this library does not support legacy pairing (using fixed PIN consisting of 4 digits)."

[https://github.com/espressif/arduino-esp32/tree/master/libraries/BluetoothSerial]
